      "name": "calcMarginalPrice",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "outcomeIndex",
          "ty_idx": 1
        }
      ],
      "return_ty_idx": 1,
      "description": "Compute the marginal price for a given outcome index.\nprice_i = exp(q_i / b) / sum(exp(q_j / b)) for all j\nUses the offset technique in log2 space (same as lmsrCost) to prevent overflow.\nReturns price in Q64.64 format."
    },
